1.26
    Added mandatory parameter: --provides. If omitted, geninitd will ask user for input.
    Added monitoring logic by pidfile, without process_name.

1.25

    Added simple messages for start and stop commands.
    Added constants for start, stop, started, stopped messages.
    Added System::InitD::Const import in System/InitD.pm.

1.24

    Added newline to System::InitD messages.
    Added new function for runner: info. Info returns more detailed output, than status.
    
1.23

    Fixed error 
    "Can't call method "user" on an undefined value at /usr/local/share/perl/5.14.2/System/InitD/Runner.pm line 282." When restarting while daemon is not running.

1.22

    Fixed "deprecated" warning, when stop called while daemon is not running.
    Makefile.PL fixed.

